history.content:
The Federal Trade Commission’s Office of Technology Research and Investigation (OTech) is hiring for a computer scientist position.  OTech provides technology expertise and conducts publishable research to inform and advance the FTC's consumer protection mission.  More details are available here: https://www.usajobs.gov/job/645883800. 

 

For researchers, this is an opportunity to work in a setting that uniquely facilitates impact.  The deadline to apply is April 19.
history.subject: [Job Opportunity] FTC OTech Computer Scientist Position
